  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6, then peel and roughly chop the<strong> ginger</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add both to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until finely chopped, then add half to a large bowl and set aside</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and discard the stems</p><p>Add the <strong>mint leaves</strong>, <strong>coriander </strong>(including the stalks)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the<strong> food processor </strong>with a splash of <strong>water </strong>and blitz again for 10-15 secs or until paste-like</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1683215950969-x200.jpg",
