    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and roughly chop 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>red onion </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped onion</strong> to the food processor with the <strong>lean beef mince </strong>and blitz for 10-20 secs or until the mixture starts to come together</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? You may need to do this in 2 batches!</p><p>Add the<strong> lean beef and onion mix</strong> to the <strong>garlic & ginger bowl</strong></p>",
