      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a lid over a medium heat with a knob of<strong> butter </strong>and let it melt</p><p>Once melted, add the<strong> basmati rice </strong>with the <strong>saffron</strong> and stir to coat in the <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Add 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [600ml]</span> <strong>water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
